<v Speaker 1>If you have amos, you know which is your vowel, no?

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:48.240
<v Speaker 2>Ah.

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:49.360
<v Speaker 1>Ah.

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:52.800
<v Speaker 1>So walk backwards.

